        <div type="letter">
            <div type="text">
                <opener>
                    <placeName><hi rend="print">Down. | Bromley. | Kent. S.E.</hi></placeName>
                    <date>Feb. 25<hi rend="superscript">th</hi></date>
                    <salute>Dear Sir</salute>
                </opener>
                <div type="transcription">
                     
<p>I am very much obliged for your kindness in sending me the results about the sexes of Trout.—<ref target="#foot.f1"/> I am anxious to ascertain approximately the proportional numbers of the sexes in any animals; but there are so many causes of error that I fear I shall not succeed.</p>
<p>With my best thanks for your information I beg leave to remain | Dear Sir | Yours faithfully | Charles Darwin</p> 
                </div>
            </div>

            
            
            
        </div>

        

        

        <div type="footnotes">
            <note xml:id="foot.f1">See the memorandum from Henry Lee, 21 January 1868 and n. 1.</note>
        </div>        
            
